section.our-services
	.our-services__container.container-fluid
		header.our-services__header
			.row
				.col-12.col-md-5
					h2.our-services__title Our Services
				.col-8.col-md-4.col-xl-5
					.our-services__short  We’ve worked with a wide array of clients across the globe to apply design fundamentals of elegance, simplicity
				.col-4.col-md-3.col-xl-2.align-self-end.align-self-md-start.text-md-right
					+arrow-link('View all', URLS.pages.services, 'our-services__more arrow-link--white')

		.our-services__accordion.accordion
			.accordion__item
				button.accordion__item-header(type="button")
					.row.align-items-md-center
						.accordion__item-title.col-11.col-md-6 Design
						.accordion__item-short.col-11.col-md-5 Our intelligent digital strategy and a pragmatic and thoughtful approach to solving business calls deliver a successful framework for both you and your audience.
				.accordion__item-body
					.row
						.accordion__item-left.col-12.col-md-6
							picture
								source(type="image/webp" srcset="img/picture/home/accordion-large.webp 1x, img/picture/home/accordion-large@2x.webp 2x")
								// 1х: 810px; 2x: 1620px
								img(src="img/picture/home/accordion-large.jpg", srcset="img/picture/home/accordion-large@2x.jpg 2x", width="810", height="530", alt="Concept")
						.accordion__item-right.col-12.col-md-6
							picture
								source(type="image/webp" srcset="img/picture/home/accordion-small.webp 1x, img/picture/home/accordion-small@2x.webp 2x")
								// 1х: 348px; 2x: 696px
								img(src="img/picture/home/accordion-small.jpg", srcset="img/picture/home/accordion-small@2x.jpg 2x", width="348", height="287", alt="Concept")

							.accordion__item-text In the design process, they create both functional and beautiful things. The team possesses unique individuality and strong qualifications and can easily translate something so abstract and visionary into a digital experience. They always put the clients first no matter how complicated the tasks are.

